{# Description: Raw copy/paste Jinja template for Spectra LS Phase 2 negative-case regression validation. #}
{# Version: 2026.04.19.2 #}
{# Last updated: 2026-04-19 #}

{# =========================
  Phase 2 Negative-Case Regression (custom_components/spectra_ls)
  Purpose: verify defer-path diagnostics are explicit when routing context is invalid.
  Workflow:
    1) Intentionally create one bad case (unknown target, unsupported path, or missing legacy source)
    2) Run actions: spectra_ls.rebuild_registry + spectra_ls.validate_contracts + spectra_ls.dump_route_trace
    3) Reload this template and confirm WARN/PASS behavior for expected defer reason
  ========================= #}

{% set s_target = 'sensor.shadow_active_target' if states['sensor.shadow_active_target'] is not none else 'sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_target' %}
{% set s_path = 'sensor.shadow_active_control_path' if states['sensor.shadow_active_control_path'] is not none else 'sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_control_path' %}

{% set active_target = states(s_target) %}
{% set active_path = states(s_path) %}
{% set parity_unresolved = state_attr(s_target,'unresolved_sources') or [] %}
{% set parity_mismatches = state_attr(s_target,'mismatches') or [] %}
{% set route_trace = state_attr(s_target,'route_trace') or {} %}
{% set route_decision = route_trace.decision if route_trace is mapping and route_trace.decision is defined else '' %}
{% set route_reason = route_trace.reason if route_trace is mapping and route_trace.reason is defined else '' %}
{% set contract_validation = state_attr(s_target,'contract_validation') or {} %}
{% set contract_valid = contract_validation.valid if contract_validation is mapping and contract_validation.valid is defined else false %}

{% set expected_defer_decisions = ['defer_no_target', 'defer_unknown_target', 'defer_unsupported_path', 'defer_not_capable'] %}
{% set observed_defer = route_decision in expected_defer_decisions %}
{% set parity_signal_present = (parity_unresolved | length) > 0 or (parity_mismatches | length) > 0 %}
{% set diagnostics_present = route_decision not in ['','none','unknown','unavailable'] and route_reason not in ['','none','unknown','unavailable'] %}

{% set healthy_route = route_decision == 'route_linkplay_tcp' and (parity_unresolved | length) == 0 and (parity_mismatches | length) == 0 and contract_valid %}

{% set verdict = 'FAIL' %}
{% if observed_defer and diagnostics_present %}
  {% set verdict = 'PASS' %}
{% elif diagnostics_present or parity_signal_present or not contract_valid %}
  {% set verdict = 'WARN' %}
{% endif %}

### Phase 2 Negative-Case Regression (`spectra_ls`)
- Result: **{{ verdict }}**
- Timestamp: **{{ now() }}**

### Inputs observed
- Active target (`{{ s_target }}`): **{{ active_target }}**
- Active path (`{{ s_path }}`): **{{ active_path }}**
- Route decision: **{{ route_decision if route_decision != '' else 'n/a' }}**
- Route reason: **{{ route_reason if route_reason != '' else 'n/a' }}**

### Negative-case signals
- Defer decision observed: **{{ observed_defer }}**
- Diagnostics present: **{{ diagnostics_present }}**
- Healthy-route observed instead of negative case: **{{ healthy_route }}**
- Parity unresolved count: **{{ parity_unresolved | length }}**
- Parity mismatch count: **{{ parity_mismatches | length }}**
- Contract valid: **{{ contract_valid }}**

### Execution semantics
- Service checkmarks in HA Actions only confirm the service call executed.
- Checkmarks do **not** prove expected negative-case route behavior; use route decision/reason above as source of truth.

### Interpretation
{% if verdict == 'PASS' %}
- Negative-case routing produced explicit defer diagnostics as expected.
{% elif healthy_route %}
- The system stayed on a healthy route (`route_linkplay_tcp`), so no negative case was actually injected.
- Intentionally create one bad condition first, then rerun services and this template.
{% elif verdict == 'WARN' %}
- Some warning signals are present, but expected defer diagnostics are incomplete. Confirm route decision/reason after rerunning services.
{% else %}
- No meaningful negative-case signal detected. Recreate a known-bad routing case and rerun the three services.
{% endif %}
